description:
This is a utility alternative to the official graphical Qt installer, for using in CI environment where an interactive UI is not usable, or just on command line.

## Troubleshooting
- False positives may occur with some antivirus software, see https://github.com/miurahr/aqtinstall/issues/423.
summary: aqt: Another (unofficial) Qt CLI Installer on multi-platforms.
author: Hiroshi Miura
